## EXISTING STRUCTURES

## ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full when harvesting
- Stop harvesting when your inventory is full.

### Could not extract due to no valid entity
- Ensure there is an entity at the specified location and that it contains the item you are trying to extract.

### Could not extract iron-plate at (0.0, 0.0)
- There is no valid entity containing iron-plate at (0.0, 0.0). Check if the coordinates are correct and if there is an entity at that location that contains the item.
